I'm now completely replacing the existing asset-handling logic. I will focus on updating the `setBoard` function to update existing spaces with new image URLs and ensuring that the `SpaceCard` component is adapted. I'll replace the existing image generation and UI components with the new logic, ensuring that the `description` field is populated correctly.


